<p>And try the test again:</p>
<pre><code class="language-bash"><div class="line">./bin/phpunit -c app --filter testInvalidJson</div></code></pre>
<p>And we <em>still</em> fail because the <code>nickname</code> field is missing. So apparently, if we
send invalid JSON, it acts like we're sending nothing. So good luck to any future
API client trying to debug this.</p>
