</p>
<p>So here's the truth about exceptions: any exception will turn into a 500 error, <em>unless</em>
that exception implements the <code>HttpExceptionInterface</code>:</p>
<p><div class="code-block-wrapper" data-code-block-guid="6525fef246">
    <div class="meta">
        <div class="actions">
            <span class="fa fa-clipboard js-activate-clipboard" data-toggle="tooltip" title="Copy Code" data-placement="top"></span>
        </div>
